    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to digital recreation of art works (such as paintings, sculpture) and other objects (furniture, relics, etc.) by reassembling known parts and filling in lacunae to create realistic, full-color hypothetical models. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
